  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个语音数据处理的完整流程图，从用户上传原始音频开始，经过转写、评估、微调，最后生成合成语音并验证。核心是要体现人工标注在闭环中的作用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User/Annotator",
        "Ingestion",
        "Transliteration Pipeline",
        "Evaluation",
        "Fine-Tune",
        "Translation",
        "Speech Synth",
        "loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我理解为：用户先提供原始音频和笔记给Ingestion模块，然后数据流向Transliteration Pipeline生成候选转写。这里Evaluation模块的作用是筛选低置信度样本回传给用户标注，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User/Annotator",
        "Ingestion",
        "Transliteration Pipeline",
        "Evaluation",
        "annotation request"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Evaluation把低置信度的样本推给用户，用户返回反馈和修正。这些被接受的数据要以版本化的JSONL格式存入Artefact Store，方便追溯。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Evaluation",
        "User/Annotator",
        "Feedback + corrections",
        "Artefact Store",
        "versioned JSONL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把Artefact Store加进来，并标注了versioned JSONL的存储关系。接下来Artefact Store会把对齐的音频文本对发给Fine-Tune模块进行模型优化？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Artefact Store",
        "Fine-Tune",
        "aligned audio/text pairs"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，Fine-Tune输出improved transcriptions给Translation模块做最终翻译，然后Speech Synth生成合成语音回传给用户。这里有个关键点：用户收到合成语音后要验证质量，如果不满意就重新回到Evaluation环节形成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Fine-Tune",
        "Translation",
        "Speech Synth",
        "User/Annotator",
        "Validate synthesis",
        "loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下闭环的细节：用户验证合成语音后，是把反馈直接给Evaluation，还是重新走一遍Ingestion？从流程效率看，直接回传Evaluation更合理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User/Annotator",
        "Evaluation",
        "Validate synthesis",
        "loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "直接回Evaluation，标注为Validate synthesis的loop。另外注意Ingestion传给Transliteration Pipeline的是dialogue objects，不是原始音频，这个区别要体现出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ingestion",
        "Transliteration Pipeline",
        "dialogue objects"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
